{{infobox Chinese|l=Yin Wood Goat|kanji=乙未|romaji=kinoto hitsuji|onyomi=otsubi|p=yǐwèi|w=i-wei|mi=i²¹ weɪ̯|y=jyut6 mei6|j=jyut6 mei6|ci=jyt̚ mei|mc=ʔit mei|oc-bs=Ɂik mei}} {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive}} '''Yin Wood Goat also known as 乙未''' (kinoto hitsuji, otsuboku no hitsuji, itsubi) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft}}.
It is the 32nd combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft}}, preceded by {{ill|Kougo|ja|甲午|12=draft}} and followed by {{ill|Boushin|ja|丙申|12=draft}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Otsu|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|12=draft}} represents yin {{ill|Wood|ja|木|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Goat|ja|未|12=draft}} represents yin {{ill|Earth|ja|土|12=draft}}, establishing a restraining relationship ({{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|五行思想#相剋（そうこく）|12=draft}}) (i.e. Wood overcomes Earth).
==Yin Wood Goat (乙未)'s Years== A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft}} that leaves a remainder of 35 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|year|ja|年|12=draft}} of {{ill|Otsumi|ja|乙未|12=draft}}. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Yin Wood Goat (乙未)'s years table''' |- ! {{ill|1st Millennium|ja|1千年紀|12=draft}} !! {{ill|2nd Millennium|ja|2千年紀|12=draft}} !! {{ill|3rd Millennium|ja|3千年紀|12=draft}} |- | * [[35]] * [[95]] * [[155]] * [[215]] * [[275]] * [[335]] * [[395]] * [[455]] * [[515]] * [[575]] * [[635]] * [[695]] * [[755]] * [[815]] * [[875]] * [[935]] * [[995]] | * [[1055]] * [[1115]] * [[1175]] * [[1235]] * [[1295]] * [[1355]] * [[1415]] * [[1475]] * [[1535]] * [[1595]] * [[1655]] * [[1715]] * [[1775]] * [[1835]] * [[1895]] * [[1955]] | * [[2015]] * [[2075]] * [[2135]] * [[2195]] * [[2255]] * [[2315]] * [[2375]] * [[2435]] * [[2495]] * [[2555]] * [[2615]] * [[2675]] * [[2735]] * [[2795]] * [[2855]] * [[2915]] * [[2975]] |} === 出来事 === * {{ill|Otsemi Jihen|ja|乙未事変|12=draft}} (1895) * {{ill|Otsemi Sensou|ja|乙未戦争|12=draft}} (1895)
==Yin Wood Goat (乙未)'s Months== In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft}} year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft}} are {{ill|Sin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|12=draft}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|12=draft}}), the month of {{ill|June|ja|6月|12=draft}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|12=draft}} of {{ill|Otsumi|ja|乙未|12=draft}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|12=draft}} (from {{ill|Minor Heat|ja|小暑|12=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Beginning of Autumn|ja|立秋|12=draft}}) as applicable.
==Yin Wood Goat (乙未)'s Days== The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|12=draft}} for {{ill|Otsumi|ja|乙未|12=draft}} is as follows. === 選日 === The day of {{ill|Otsumi|ja|乙未|12=draft}} is the 3rd day of {{ill|Ten Ten Ichijou|ja|天一天上|12=draft}}.
==See Also== *{{prefix}} *{{intitle}}
