==Yin Wood Goat (乙未)'s Days== The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} for {{ill|Otsumi|ja|乙未|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is as follows. === 選日 === The day of {{ill|Otsumi|ja|乙未|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is the 3rd day of {{ill|Ten Ten Ichijou|ja|天一天上|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
